OL,5, First-time house buyers could find it  
OL,6, more difficult to get onto the property
OL,7, ladder due to fewer mortgage deals with
OL,8, smaller deposits being on offer.       
OL,10,FFigures from research body Moneyfacts  
OL,11,Fshow there were 137 mortgage offers at 
OL,12,F95% loan-to-value on Monday, compared  
OL,13,Fto 347 at the start of 2022.           
OL,15,FThe downward trend of such deals was   
OL,16,Faccelerated after the mini-budget      
OL,17,Fsparked turmoil on the markets.        
OL,19,FMortgage interest rates hit 14-year    
OL,20,Fhighs, but have since begun to fall.   
